{"product_id":"upcircle-beauty-face-mask-with-kaolin-clay-60ml","title":"UpCircle Beauty Face Mask with Kaolin Clay 60ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eAn award-winning gently-detoxifying clay face mask to fight blackheads, minimise pores and prevent breakouts. Skin is left feeling cleansed, refreshed and balanced.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis clarifying kaolin clay face mask is suitable for all skin types. The olive powder is combined with rejuvenating white kaolin clay, coconut powder and baobab oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspiring, upcycling, uplifting: This detoxifying face mask is made with the finely-ground powder of discarded olive stones, a natural by-product of the olive oil industry and a powerful anti-inflammatory.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWinner of the CEW Responsibility Award 2022, winner in the Beauty Shortlist Awards 2021 and finalist in the Vogue Beauty Awards 2020.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to damp skin in a thin layer and relax for ten minutes. Rinse with warm water or a damp cloth to reveal fresh, cleansed skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Kaolin, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Milk Powder, Olea Europaea (Olive) Leaf Powder*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Butter*, Glyceryl Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glycerin, Adansonia Digitata (Baobab) Seed Oil, Curcuma Longa (Turmeric) Root Oil, Citrus Limonum (Lemon) Peel Oil, Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Oil, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract*, Cistus Ladaniferus Leaf Oil, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Oil, Zingiber Cassumunar (Plai) Root Oil, Cedrus Atlantica (Cedarwood) Bark Oil, Tocopherol, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Sucrose Stearate, Coco Glucoside, Coconut Alcohol, Dehydroacetic Acid, Lactic Acid, Benzyl Alcohol, Limonene**, Citral**, Linalool**, Geraniol**. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organically-grown ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e**Natural constituent of essential oils listed\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e99% NATURAL INGREDIENTS\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHandmade | Social Good | Recycled Materials | Zero Waste | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources | Non Toxic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"UpCircle Beauty","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51132854501703,"sku":null,"price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/upcircle-beauty-face-mask-with-kaolin-clay-60ml-860452.png?v=1740808673","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/upcircle-beauty-face-mask-with-kaolin-clay-60ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}